David M. Maura CFAExecutive Chairman, Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships45$11,182,497As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. David M. Maura, CFA served as the Managing Director and an Executive Vice President of Investments at HRG Group, Inc. since October 2011 until November 28,  2016. Mr. Maura served as a Vice President and Director of Investments at Harbinger Capital Partners and joined it in November 2006. Prior to Harbinger Capital Partners, Mr. Maura served as an exclusive Consultant for Harbinger Capital Partners, providing fundamental and valuation analysis as well as idea generation ... within the consumer related industries. Before joining Harbinger, he was a Managing Director at First Albany Capital, where he focused on distressed debt and special situations primarily in the consumer products and retail sectors. Prior to First Albany, Mr. Maura was a Director and Senior High Yield Research Analyst in Global High Yield Research at Merrill Lynch & Co. He was employed at BofA Merrill Lynch, Research Division, Wells Fargo Securities, LLC, Research Division and Gleacher & Company, Inc., Research Division. He was a Vice President and Senior Analyst at Wachovia Securities where he covered various consumer product, service and retail companies. He began his career in finance at ZPR Investment Management as a Financial Analyst. He serves as the SB/RH Holdings, LLC. He has been the Executive Chairman of Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. since July 2011 and served as its Interim Chairman from June 2010 to July 2011 and has been its Director since June 2010. He has been a Director of HRG Group, Inc. (formerly Harbinger Group Inc.) since May 12, 2011. He served as a Director of Russell Hobbs, Inc. until January 23, 2007. He served as a Director of Salton Inc. from June 2006 to January 23, 2007. He was designated as a C.F.A. in 1995. Mr. Maura graduated from Stetson University in 1994 with a Bachelor of Science degree in Business Administration.Read Full Background




