Insider Activity


Individual




David M. Maura



Mr. David M. Maura, CFA, is Director, Managing Director & EVP-Investments at HRG Group, Inc., Executive Chairman at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. and Chairman at SB/RH Holdings LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at HRG Group, Inc. 
Mr. Maura was previously employed as Chairman by Spectrum Brands, Inc., Vice President & Director of Investments by Harbinger Capital Partners LLC, Chairman by Salton, Inc., Managing Director & Senior Research Analyst by Broadpoint Capital Inc., Director & Senior High Yield Research Analyst by Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc. /Old/, Vice President by Wachovia Securities LLC, Vice President & Senior Analyst by Wachovia Securities, Inc., and Financial Analyst by ZPR Investment Management, Inc. He also served on the board at Applica, Inc., Ferrous Resources Ltd. and Russell Hobbs, Inc. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Stetson University.



